{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/98955", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/98955/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/98955/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/98955/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/98955", "id": 1294692906, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M5NK3Iq", "number": 98955, "title": "API Request: pointer::[op]_assign", "user": {"login": "Lokathor", "id": 5456384, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjU0NTYzODQ=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5456384?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor", "html_url": "https://github.com/Lokathor", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Lokathor/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 630652267, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2MzA2NTIyNjc=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-feature-request", "name": "C-feature-request", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: A feature request, i.e: not implemented / a PR."}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2022-07-05T19:41:01Z", "updated_at": "2023-02-05T09:05:45Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "It is often the case that you want to edit a pointer that you've got during a loop. In this case you need code like\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nloop {\r\n  // do work\r\n  ptr = ptr.add(1);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever, the same as we've got `Add::add`, we also have `AddAssign::add_assign`. Adding to pointers is `unsafe`, so we can't provide the AddAssign trait impl directly, but we can provide a method of the same name (as we already did with `add`).\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nloop {\r\n  // do work\r\n  ptr.add_assign(1);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nSimilarly, `sub` and `offset` can have the same \"_assign\" treatment.", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/98955/reactions", "total_count": 1, "+1": 1, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/98955/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}